data.description: Outstanding location between Redmond and Bend. Great horse property. Fenced and cross fenced.  6.00 acres of COI irrigation, private well, several outbuildings, tool shed, storage shed level ground. Single level home lovingly cared for, warm and inviting family room with wood burning stove, solar water heater, new heat pump, new furnace within six months, newer roof, new disposal.  Farm deferral, owners currently rent out pastures. Great potential as to farm deferral uses.  Schedule your showing today!
